<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.4.3">
<l>pēycci mulaiyuṇṇak kaṇṭu piṉṉaiyum nillāteṉ ṉeñca</l>
<l>māycciya rellāruṅ kūṭi yaḻaikkavum nāṉmulai tantēṉ</l>
<l>kāycciṉa nīroṭu nelli kaṭārattiṟ pūrittu vaittēṉ</l>
<l>vāytta pukaḻmaṇi vaṇṇā mañcaṉa māṭanī vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Seeing when [you] drank from the breast of the demoness,</l>
<l>afterward, my heart not waiting, even though all the cowherdesses</l>
<l rend="indent">had gathered together [and] cried out,</l>
<l>I gave [you my] breast.</l>
<l>I have filled a pot with gooseberries and boiled water.</l>
<l>O Sapphire-hued lord with flourishing glory!</l>
<l>Come to bathe in [your] ceremonial bath.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
